Thank you for all the sweet messages asking if I’m alright because I haven’t really been posting. You all are so lovely to worry about me. To be honest, we have been shooting the anniversary shows #yr50 @youngandrestlesscbs so, we aren’t allowed to post and I’ve been moving my place in L. A. And setting up my Air bnb in West Hollywood #theleelist @crystalfambrini while in construction in Nashville. I’m so excited for this weekend and I will be posting! ❤️🥰 #weddingplanning #wedding #caketasting #decoration #notmywedding photo by @kristybelcherphotography dress @theshowroomnashville

I was sent this picture a week ago and it’s now what I will look at whenever I have a down day. This moment was captured when I was so filled with emotion, love, surprise and wonder. I don’t smile often in pictures because I don’t think I look good but this unfiltered picture (I didn’t touch it) makes me feel differently. I will never forget this moment as long as I live. @youngandrestlesscbs @thetalkcbs @sony @mattykane1 @christianjleblanc You sure know how to blow a girl away. And a big shout out to my dear friend @drbilldorfman for creating this smile. After watching all the flashbacks over the years, thank God I met you for so many reasons. ❤️❤️❤️ @daytimeemmys @cbstv

Happy Birthday to one of my favorite people on earth, my first born, my best friend, my rock. You are such an extraordinary person, that I cherish and am grateful for every moment of my life. I love your voraciousness for knowledge and understanding. I love hearing your ideas and I love our daily downloads. It has been one of life’s greatest gifts being your mother and being so close to you. You are a beacon of shining light in this world and I am so thrilled for all your accomplishments and for what is to come! I love you to the moon and back @austinrecht 🎂🌟❤️

As Mother’s Day is coming to a close, I want to thank my children for making me a mom, a step- mom, a mother in law to be, a Gigi and to my mom, thank you for making me your daughter. To all of you for teaching me about the depth of love and for showing me how big my heart can grow. Thank you for accepting me, supporting me, remembering me, writing me such beautiful cards and letters, making each day amazing and growing with me and buying me my favorite treats.  Thank you for loving me and laughing with me. You all are my everything ❤️❤️❤️ @austinrecht @swipertruelove @emilyrecht @linnyloutype1 @tone_ya @sillysuzieq #momlife #momslove #mothersday

This is a big birthday. I am so grateful for every year and for my family, friends and work, who make my life so filled with fun and love. Thank you to my family and friends who show up, consistently. You know what that means to me. I love you all so much and thank you for all the thoughtful things that you do. You mean the world to me. It is not lost on me that age is a gift denied to many. Grateful for every day and all the amazing memories. #thebig6 #family#love#friends#birthdays photo : @kristybelcherphotography 💕

Is it possible to be in love with a driveway? Well, I am. This driveway represents that I’m home. It’s the start of my peace. My Mother is at the end of this driveway and my animals. My family gathers for beautiful memories at the end of this driveway. This driveway is more than just that, it’s my road to happiness. ❤️ photo: @genereedphotography all clothing: @moocountry

Thank you @prenuvo for my full body MRI and peace of mind. I feel so much better knowing what is going on in my body. I’m usually someone who is very anxious doing an MRI, my doctor of record, gave me a little something to keep me calm but the tube is much bigger than a normal MRI and you can watch TV! I got my results in under two weeks and a nurse called me to go through them all. Happy to report just a couple of minor things but I’m going to my internist tomorrow morning to go through the findings with him too. I feel we must be in charge of our health and healthcare and this is my way. Use my name TRACEY for $300 off. Let me know how it goes! #health #myhealth #knowledge #information #healthiswealth FOR ONLINE APPOINTMENTS. CLICK HERE! For on-line bookings to work people need to click the full link we provided: Prenuvo.com/Tracey 🌸💕

Happy Birthday to my baby boy. @swipertruelove To the little boy who loved to sit in my lap, twirl my hair and watch the world to the amazing man you are today. Love our laughs, language we only understand, to our deep talks over crazy expensive vegan  meals, to always knowing the best thing to order on any menu. I wish all the wonderful things life has to offer. I love you so mush! Xoxox Momma ❤️

We lost the soul of my Ranch this morning. Standing Ovation or Ovi, as he was known as, passed away with me by his side. This is the hard part for loving these beautiful souls so fiercely. We had 10 incredible years together and my boys and my whole family loved him deeply. Ovi, I hope you are doing canter pirouettes in heaven with Buddha by your side. #standingovation #freisian #love 💔❤️
